{"tid":2308744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普據報暗示若今屆選舉未能翻盤將再戰下屆","createTime":"2020-12-02T06:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T05:27:19.000Z","uid":18569,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a61495684cba74260d9072f39ae008c8ed2321d5","tid":2308744,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T06:11:38.000Z","msg":"特朗普據報暗示若今屆選舉未能翻盤將再戰下屆<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普至今未有承認在大選中落敗，<span class=\"red\">美國傳媒報道</span>，特朗普當地星期二晚在白宮舉行聖誕派對時發表演講，形容過了了不起的四年，並正努力再做多四年，否則四年後再見，意味他即使未能在今屆選舉翻盤，亦打算再戰下屆大選。特朗普一直指控選舉舞弊，他的競選陣營亦繼續提出法律訴訟，挑戰選舉結果。不過，司法部長巴爾與特朗普唱反調，認為目前無證據顯示，存在足以改變大選結果的大規模舞弊行為。分析說，巴爾的說法，對特朗普來說是一次重大打擊。<br />\n<br />\n2020-12-02 14:01:10"},{"pid":"c8c865140cd120b12214f33e3fb79f35c61f4bc6","tid":2308744,"uid":371558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T06:12:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c105275a90ace9bb931074db676a9061f9ea43f","tid":2308744,"uid":2002,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T06:12:45.000Z","msg":"美國傳媒=ccn"},{"pid":"bc28bf88fdd58cdcec5e82f98e1cb1c3d9ed2a50","tid":2308744,"uid":40171,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"又Fake News <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲橋段老唔老土啲呀"},{"pid":"91c90daef9a8cc8d5ff5481b9e6c5eb18395fc31","tid":2308744,"uid":243380,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"英國研究中國製造韓國起源美國傳媒"},{"pid":"a67ca7676d2f107c0f3932556ffead7ef2cdfe4f","tid":2308744,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91c90daef9a8cc8d5ff5481b9e6c5eb18395fc31","tid":2308744,"uid":243380,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"英國研究中國製造韓國起源美國傳媒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T06:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif